Looks like you did well for yourself, Jeff.
Maybe it was worth the money.
In my experience buses that are "free" generally don't
stay "free".
In fact they generally are only good to be freed of
all useful parts then sent to bus heaven.
Keep us informed on your successes & adventures.
:-)
